node.text:
🍁
Let's be wild again,
In these mighty mountains.
Let's be explorers again,
In these contemporary times.

Let's create the history again,
By repeating it's essence.
Let's take the road again,
That's never been taken.

Let's do the impossible again,
And make it possible.
Let's be wild again
And be, never the same.
~Priya Bihani

node.text:
Oh my mind! Oh my mind!
Help me! Help me brood!
Help me introspect! 
Help me ruminate!
What am I?
Black and White 
Where choices are so slight!
therby so easy on the mind.
Or the colors of different kind
A high spirited, yet so confused
Whether right is wrong, or wrong is right
Never ending chaos runs through the mind
All the time! All the time!
 ~Priya Bihani
